(48, 1, '2020-04-09 17:08:31', '2020-04-09 17:08:31', '<!-- wp:image {\"id\":49,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost/mobile%20blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/11.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-49\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A new dualcamera system captures more of what you see and love. The fastest chip ever in a smartphone and allday battery life let you do more and charge less. And the highestquality video in a smartphone, so your memories look better&nbsp;than&nbsp;ever.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'iPhone 11: Just the right amount of everything.', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'iphone-11-just-the-right-amount-of-everything', '', '', '2020-04-09 18:20:00', '2020-04-09 18:20:00', '', 0, 'http://localhost/mobile%20blog/?p=48', 0, 'post', '', 0),
