(56, 1, '2020-04-09 18:25:32', '2020-04-09 18:25:32', '<!-- wp:image {\"id\":31,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost/mobile%20blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/s20.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-31\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>There arent many phones out there, from Samsung or other OEMs, that use Ultra in their names. It seems Samsung realized that it would have to do justice to this word if it decided to call the top-of-the-line 2020 flagship the Galaxy S20 Ultra. It became clear on the day Samsung unveiled the Galaxy S20 series that it&nbsp;meant business with the Ultra.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Samsung Galaxy S20 Ultra review: Too exceptional for most customers', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '29-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-04-09 18:25:32', '2020-04-09 18:25:32', '', 29, 'http://localhost/mobile%20blog/index.php/2020/04/09/29-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(58, 1, '2020-04-10 11:08:29', '2020-04-10 11:08:29', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Integrating corporate management and sustainable development is an issue of increasing importance in the business world, amid increasing expectations for social and environmental responsibility. In response, we have been improving the process of collecting stakeholders\' ideas and setting up corporate-wide vision and strategies for sustainable development. We have designated economic, environmental and social responsibilities as the key elements of our sustainable management. We are committed to continuing to identify our various stakeholders, build positive relationships with them and ultimately enhance our value for both the company and the stakeholders. Visit: <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.samsung.com/us/1/\" target=\"_blank\">Android</a> |  <a href=\"https://www.apple.com/\">iOS</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '6-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-04-10 11:08:29', '2020-04-10 11:08:29', '', 6, 'http://localhost/mobile%20blog/index.php/2020/04/10/6-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(59, 1, '2020-04-10 11:09:37', '2020-04-10 11:09:37', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Integrating corporate management and sustainable development is an issue of increasing importance in the business world, amid increasing expectations for social and environmental responsibility. In response, we have been improving the process of collecting stakeholders\' ideas and setting up corporate-wide vision and strategies for sustainable development. We have designated economic, environmental and social responsibilities as the key elements of our sustainable management. We are committed to continuing to identify our various stakeholders, build positive relationships with them and ultimately enhance our value for both the company and the stakeholders. Visit: <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.samsung.com/us/1/\" target=\"_blank\">Android</a> |  <a href=\"https://www.apple.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iOS</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '6-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-04-10 11:09:37', '2020-04-10 11:09:37', '', 6, 'http://localhost/mobile%20blog/index.php/2020/04/10/6-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
